Go to www.kreutzers.eu and get a permanent 20% Discount on all eatable products and 10€ shipping discount for free. Its called  the KREUTZERS PRIME membership, which usually costs 99€ for 2 years. Insert the code: “nordicchefs” in PRIME CODE field at the customer registration (log in), and then you have 24 month PRIME for free.
Shipps EU/Germany
